00:31:36.144 --> 00:31:37.145
Merci.

00:31:41.024 --> 00:31:42.276
Je t'ai manqué ?

00:31:50.909 --> 00:31:53.412
Donc, tu as eu de la compagnie ?

00:31:54.621 --> 00:31:55.706
Possible.

00:31:57.958 --> 00:32:00.043
